name: 20 WINDY ARRIVALS AND DEPARTURES! Calgary Airport Plane Spotting Runway 29
description:
29 operations at Calgary International Airport are always fun to watch, since most traffic is (usually) condensed onto one runway! Here are 20 arrivals and departures on runway 29 a few weeks back, featuring some of YYC's regular traffic battling some chinook winds!
